      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex,</p>\n<p>If you don\u2019t mind i would like to now how can i insert a message uploaded from TP.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-English\" data-username=\"Alex\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"1284\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/48/1331_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"><a href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/t/app-design-questions-sounds-indicators-zoom-levels/1284/2\">App Design Questions. Sounds, indicators, zoom levels</a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>We flash the chart before the change too (better tha a message in my opinion). You could easily add messages in about 20 seconds to each of your workouts but you would have to follow the workout in our app. I can explain if you want.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thanks,<br>\nNuno</p>",
